data.description: Welcome to the desirable community of Crestview Manor. NOW UNTIL DEC 10th, $5000 in closing costs from seller! As you enter your new home, you'll be greeted by a spacious entrance that leads to a warm and inviting living area, separate dining and breakfast spaces, and a generously sized kitchen that overlooks the living room - an entertainer's dream. The upper level boasts four generously sized bedrooms, a laundry room, and two full baths. Step outside to a serene private retreat, perfect for family or outdoor gatherings. The fenced-in backyard features a spacious patio deck for your relaxation and entertainment. Adding to the appeal, the home has a two-car garage additional parking, and a beautifully landscaped yard. Freshly painted and carpeted, this fantastic home is one you don't want to miss.
